ity\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique approach\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"over 90 boats\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The broadcast flitted between the athletes being shown on their boats to various dances and artistic performances before the end of the ceremony at the Palais du Trocadero.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The broadcast\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"their boats\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"various dances\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic performances\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"the Palais\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest updates on the 2024 Olympic Games After the Olympic flag was raised upside down,Celine Dionstole the showwith a sublime performance to end the ceremony.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"latest updates\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"Celine Dionstole\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the showwith\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"a sublime performance\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Adlington, who won two golds and two bronze medals during her Olympic swimming career, said she would have preferred the ceremony to be held inside the stadium.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adlington_Hall\", \"score\": 0.9998870791919435, \"rank\": 8.63011690203801e-05, \"text\": \"Adlington\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adlington_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adlington_Hall\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"two bronze medals\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic swimming career\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's one of those it's a different experience when you are watching it on telly to when you are out there,' she said in the BBC studio in Paris.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.992751936615736, \"rank\": 0.007298313846038557, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.89937904768153e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different experience\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro's Head\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"punchy analysis\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"transfer talk\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"his take\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the week's biggest stories\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an open goal\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The weather is not helping, it has not stopped raining so I think being cold and it's just one of those where it's slightly tarnished the experience.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The weather\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It wasn't my favourite opening ceremony, I have to admit, just because I think it was so different and so ambitious that I think I am probably stuck in my ways.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favourite opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"my ways\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I like the stadium, I like when it's all together and I like when you can see different things going off whereas this felt a bit disjointed in parts.'\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"different things\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"parts\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former United States sprinter Michael Johnson, who was also working as a BBC pundit for the opening ceremony, claims some spectators were also 'going long periods without being entertained'.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9988057323395912, \"rank\": 0.001170123950191411, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.992751936615736, \"rank\": 0.007298313846038557, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"some spectators\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"long periods\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was different,' Johnson said of the ceremony in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9666319647041828, \"rank\": 0.030965011809156, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9518895133050684, \"rank\": 0.044245471852056274, \"text\": \"French\", \"typ