hat their experience was.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"their experience\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Because I think from what I was getting from some people that I know who were out there, there were some long periods where they were not really entertained, they did not get to see anything.\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"some long periods\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you are in a stadium, you have that sound and all of the live action and entertainment going on in front of you, so I am not sure what their experience was.'\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"that sound\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"the live action\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"entertainment\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"their experience\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest news onFacebook\", \"from\